sequenceDiagram
    participant Source as External Source
    participant Adapter as Source Adapter
    participant SM as SourceManager
    participant EB as EventBus
    participant TR as TopicRegistry
    participant TS as TimeSeriesRepository
    participant MR as ModuleRegistry
    participant Mod as System Module
    participant PG as PostgreSQL
    participant Influx as InfluxDB
    participant WS as WebSocket
    participant UI as React UI

    Source->>Adapter: Raw telemetry message
    Adapter->>Adapter: Normalize raw data
    Adapter->>SM: NormalizedMessage
    SM->>EB: publish message.received

    EB->>TR: register or update topic
    TR->>PG: save topic metadata
    TR->>EB: publish topic.discovered if new

    EB->>TS: write telemetry
    TS->>Influx: persist value

    EB->>MR: dispatch message.received
    MR->>Mod: handle event
    Mod->>PG: save module output

    EB->>WS: publish live update
    WS->>UI: push topic/message update